s </strong></b><span>:&nbsp;</span></h3><p dir=3D"ltr"><span>In Spearman's =
rank correlation, the process involves converting the original data into ra=
nks. This is done to assess the monotonic relationship between two variable=
s without relying on the specific numerical values of the data points. </sp=
an></p>
